#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:735
msgid "The function signature should be as follows:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:739
msgid ""
"Return a :class:`dict` of key-value pairs to apply to the feed URI using :"
"ref:`printf-style string formatting <python:old-string-formatting>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:742
msgid ""
"default key-value pairs  Specifically:  -   ``batch_id``: ID of the file "
"batch. See     :setting:`FEED_EXPORT_BATCH_ITEM_COUNT`.      If :setting:"
"`FEED_EXPORT_BATCH_ITEM_COUNT` is ``0``, ``batch_id``     is always ``1``.  "
"-   ``batch_time``: UTC date and time, in ISO format with ``:``     replaced "
"with ``-``.      See :setting:`FEED_EXPORT_BATCH_ITEM_COUNT`.  -   ``time``: "
"``batch_time``, with microseconds set to ``0``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:742
msgid "default key-value pairs"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:744
msgid "Specifically:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:746
msgid ""
"``batch_id``: ID of the file batch. See :setting:"
"`FEED_EXPORT_BATCH_ITEM_COUNT`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:749
msgid ""
"If :setting:`FEED_EXPORT_BATCH_ITEM_COUNT` is ``0``, ``batch_id`` is always "
"``1``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:752
msgid ""
"``batch_time``: UTC date and time, in ISO format with ``:`` replaced with ``-"
"``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:755
msgid "See :setting:`FEED_EXPORT_BATCH_ITEM_COUNT`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:757
msgid "``time``: ``batch_time``, with microseconds set to ``0``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:760
msgid "source spider of the feed items"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:763
msgid ""
"The function should return a new dictionary, modifying the received "
"``params`` in-place is deprecated."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:766
msgid ""
"For example, to include the :attr:`name <scrapy.Spider.name>` of the source "
"spider in the feed URI:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:769
msgid "Define the following function somewhere in your project:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:771
msgid ""
"# myproject/utils.py\n"
"def uri_params(params, spider):\n"
"    return {**params, \"spider_name\": spider.name}"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:777
msgid "Point :setting:`FEED_URI_PARAMS` to that function in your settings:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:779
msgid ""
"# myproject/settings.py\n"
"FEED_URI_PARAMS = \"myproject.utils.uri_params\""
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:784
msgid "Use ``%(spider_name)s`` in your feed URI::"
